Sputnik makes any home smart and any yard safe.

The “Sputnik: Smart Home”(Envoi) app allows you to:
- see what's going on in your yard;
- receive calls from the intercom wherever you are;
- open the door with one click. 

Please make sure you've paid service fee to your provider to use the basic app functions.
 You may also buy a suscription to use additional smart functions.

Premium subscription expands the intercom functions:
- archive of video recordings from the intercom;
- temporary access codes for couriers, relatives and friends;
- facial recognition for entry into the building, without a key or code

Korter — service for buying property directly from real estate developers in Azerbaijan, Georgia, Kazakhstan, Moldova, Poland and Romania. We work with most of top-develoers and have all information about all their apartments and houses in sale from them. All offers are carefully moderated by the Korter team.

On our platform you can buy only homes. We work with international clients especially in Batumi and Tbilisi, but can provide our service if you are interested in real estate in other regions.

We have long-time experience with property investments with clients from the globe.

Apartments and houses listings in Korter:
- high quality photos and renders of every property;
- regular photos of construction progress;
- property layouts and accurate prices;
- easy and convenient property search using comprehensive filters;
- interested in apartments from developers you trust? – use search by developer;
- property locations on the interactive 3D map including all the critical infrastructure of comfortable life.

Choosing homes on Korter — you always choose from all actual listings from all developers!

Календарь беременности - полезное и удобное приложение для будущих мамочек.

Наше приложение для беременных имеет следующие функции :
- Трекер беременности по неделям / месяцам;
- Советы на каждый день и неделю в виде небольших полезных статей;
- Учет изменения веса и размера животика;
- Расчет текущей недели беременности и срок родов;
- Счетчик шевелений малыша;
- Счетчик схваток;
- Дневник беременности с возможностью: указать настроение, написать заметку, поставить напоминание о враче или приёме таблеток;

Для работы нашего приложения для беременных необходимо подключение к интернету.
